{"tid":567573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"飛的檢獲iPhone 7 好心男欲交機主反被爆樽","createTime":"2018-02-21T04:02:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-22T01:17:49.000Z","uid":83518,"like":240,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"915810d71ef7dbbadbc1413a51a642c41cabcf7f","tid":567573,"uid":83518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T04:02:26.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】一名姓張33歲男子凌晨三時許，於紅磡德民街遭約四名男子圍毆，事主受傷致電報警。他稱較早前與姓沈33歲妻子，乘的士從尖沙嘴返回紅磡住所途中，在座椅上檢獲一部iPhone 7手機，其後電話響起遂相約機主取回手機，夫婦當到達約定地點等候交收期間，機主及數名男子突衝出用啤酒樽向他施襲毆打，並將手機奪回，四散逃去，救護員趕至將傷者送院治理，警方正展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/home/飛的檢獲iphone-7-好心男欲交機主反被爆樽-234500645.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fhome%2F%E9%A3%9B%E7%9A%84%E6%AA%A2%E7%8D%B2iphone-7-%E5%A5%BD%E5%BF%83%E7%94%B7%E6%AC%B2%E4%BA%A4%E6%A9%9F%E4%B8%BB%E5%8F%8D%E8%A2%AB%E7%88%86%E6%A8%BD-234500645.html&d=PkCvH6rt5OWO8IJPVKTzOLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=dd3d5905\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/home/飛的檢獲iphone-7-好心男欲交機主反被爆樽-234500645.html</a>"},{"pid":"d8ec386940ec44e74d98421f63ecdc6619e5d898","tid":567573,"uid":73043,"like":827,"dislike":3,"score":824,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T04:03:39.000Z","msg":"所以話 香港地做好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4524d803eba3432f402971c3a00849b8035fe06","tid":567573,"uid":31,"like":273,"dislike":66,"score":207,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T04:04:17.000Z","msg":"執到電話一係賣一係扔左佢啦 仲比返人 咁撚大個人跌電話都抵死啦"},{"pid":"647de8a1964efaf857dbc969cda73811db4409f7","tid":567573,"uid":41818,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T04:04:58.000Z","msg":"香港地執到都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ff3d172e3486d72c68c7674d3e9e279f9e24608","tid":567573,"uid":89478,"like":28,"dislike":82,"score":-54,"quote":{"pid":"d8ec386940ec44e74d98421f63ecdc6619e5d898","tid":567573,"uid":73043,"like":827,"dislike":3,"score":824,"citedBy":